                                        h4.icon-subheader.margin-top-60 Join and get on the waitlist
                                        p Due to overwhelming interest, we are currently only activating a few profiles every week. Join now to get on our waitlist.

                                    .col-md-4.text-center
                                        img.img-responsive(src="images/icon_device_lg.png", alt="Icon Device")
                                        h4.icon-subheader.margin-top-60 Download the app & complete your profile
                                        p Download the app, complete your profile and let temporary jobs come to you without applications or interviews.

                                    .col-md-4.text-center
                                        img.img-responsive(src="images/icon_tuxedo.png", alt="Icon Tuxedo")
